    • getPDFPageCount

      public static int getPDFPageCount(String fileName)
      Get the number of pages in a PDF file. This is handy when the number of pages in a PDF document is unknown.

      Returns 0 on error.

      PDF only! Other file types will return 0

      Returns:

    • isDocumentAlreadyRefiledInQueue

      public static boolean isDocumentAlreadyRefiledInQueue(String filename, int queueId)
      Checks if a document with the given filename has already been refiled in the specified queue.
      Parameters:
      filename - The original filename of the document.
      queueId - The ID of the queue where the document might have been refiled.
      Returns:
      true if a document with the refiled name exists in the queue's refile directory, false otherwise.
